Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.53,0:00:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露出一副還在做夢的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:00:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎不小心睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好  常有的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想貼身的東西還是脫掉比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且出了一身冷汗  身子也幫你擦過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你照顧我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.91,0:01:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  沒做奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年希望姐姐對你做點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.89,0:01:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如這樣的  還有那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想自己丟臉的樣子被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  用不著害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輕鬆一些就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從小就患有嗜睡症了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道病因是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不知何時就會倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有時會感到些許不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來和大家在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是最能讓我安心的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是我的容身之所嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說Little Busters也是唯一能讓我放下心來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到不合群的我  現在也能被夥伴們圍繞著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是現在能一直持續下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在能  一直
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為十分快樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心想現在要是不會結束就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生過好多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試膽大會  首次的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤薄餅派對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來谷同學成為夥伴後一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介是在五月中旬開始玩棒球的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六月二十日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來谷同學加入Little Busters後才過了不到一個月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得已經過了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去也有過相同的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時也在下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你對現狀沒有任何想法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是在和可愛的女性獨處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你這麼一說還真是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳加速了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒心跳加速才怪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快說哎喲心快跳出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快說哎喲太爽了  真爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才可是睡在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你把身子暖起來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹君真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐最大的樂趣就是看你驚慌失措的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼喜歡捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我喜歡理樹君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  就這張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  理樹  到你出牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  發什麼呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才就心不在焉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你樣子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是  自從被來谷照顧了回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一直心神不定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  被來谷照顧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為平時的那個所以睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛…是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴你明白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  理樹你迷上那個來谷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的  你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  你現在感受到了心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你別這樣  謙吾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的臉和你所說的台詞不搭邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從以前就在想了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該去戀愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為情所困  為情所傷  人才能有所成長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛會讓理樹變為成熟的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別誤會啊  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣的話  理樹你喜歡誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有真心喜歡過一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼恭介你又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法回答也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹喜歡的人果然是恭介嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是恭介啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜歡理樹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹喜歡的是來谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會喜歡上那種恐怖的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦白吧  你迷上了來谷的哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛是不需要理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣才是愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等等啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  大貧民才玩到一半呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女心  海底針啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我們會全面支持理樹的戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰名是Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little LoveLove Hunters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LoveLove
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hunters？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰名變更為LoliLoli Hunters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在這裡冷場了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又沒說我是Loli
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說先把恭介是不是Loli這個問題放一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能放一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是問題中心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是剛好看見這部漫畫而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是也挺好的嗎  Loli
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不會介意這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  女僕控
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是注意到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在盯著女僕看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是  只是剛好看到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後是謙吾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡的是巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢  蠢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你稍微有點動搖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要再看一回嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊  看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.14,up,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛發現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把（21）這樣寫出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像不像Loli
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,326)\fs21}ロリ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是有點像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:59.25,up,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想變成Loli啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣等我21歲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫「真人（21）」的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就變成「真人Loli」了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想變成21歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綜上所述
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綜什麼所述啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是告白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想好作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來放煙火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡有個煙火彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是以前旅行時得到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給一個勉強能糊口的煙火師傅幫過忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這傢伙發射到夜空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不太明白你說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓理樹和來谷在夜晚的校舍中獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我們用這個煙火給他們製造點氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綻放在夜空裡的盛大煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不情願也會墜入愛河的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙火放完之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人在一片怡靜之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相傾述…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛  愛  愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛  愛  愛  愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛  愛  愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛  愛  愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是被稱作浪漫大總統的謙吾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個稱號我可是第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也給鈴和神北  能美  三枝還有西園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看這盛大的煙火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  烤薄餅派對的回禮也還沒回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用煙火來當回禮也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說煙火大會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家肯定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  女生都很喜歡煙火的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:11:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有異議
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好  來制定計劃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是真人和謙吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼想  這都是個魯莽的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在認真思考這些胡來的主意的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才最讓人興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們和過去相比一點也沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題吧  這雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到晚上一定會停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六月二十日  今晚進行煙火大會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  這樣總算能湊合一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我們也找來了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是剩餘的煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  從教室觀賞煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是難得一見的情景哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  這麼大根要怎樣點火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別怕  包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅教過我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然就一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙幹的事情總是讓人不安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  按原計劃由理樹把女生們引到目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製造出和來谷兩人獨處的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  開始準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我們的禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  禮物是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時還要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  大姐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把美少女們引誘到黑燈瞎火的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是要圖謀不軌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有你說的那麼可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走  出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  我並不打算跟來谷兩人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  好像就是這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳聞中無頭亡靈所出現的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來想說這謠言是三枝同學帶頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果連本人都跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這  這情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火點不起來  混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用氣勢  用氣勢點著它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到開始的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨…停了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊  恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹君吃驚的樣子  還是那麼好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用這火來點  YEAHYEAH
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  順利點著了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:15:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是想讓我看這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這群笨蛋想出的這主意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還挺有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  是時候發射壓軸的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來一發！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝啊衝啊  衝上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙火萬歲！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能認識到這樣棒的笨蛋夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是難得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H00593B00&\bord0\an5\fs20\move(360,103,362,100)\t(0,2100,\fs22)\1a&50&}致理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H00593B00&\bord0\an5\fs23\frz-1\move(265,180,255,185)\t(0,2100,\fs26)\1a&50&}告白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告白？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:18:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介他…問我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「你有真心喜歡過一個人嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是  你有沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一句話也說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅被眼前所陶醉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此漂亮的來谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是第一次看見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:18:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡的是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  今天不是二十號而是二十一號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個鐘壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是二十號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十號是昨天才對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介昨晚也說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「六月二十日  今晚進行煙火大會」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做夢做糊塗了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:26.42,up,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不是昨天沾濕的痕跡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這雨還真能下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是繼續這樣下去  明天也沒法練習棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:40.58,up,NTP,0,0,0,,新聞播報完畢  下面是六月二十日的天氣預報
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到午後六點為止  降水機率達70%
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了與昨天一模一樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天也看過這副景象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露出一副還在做夢的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逐漸消失的雪花  你會就此忘記嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  想要永遠留在這裡
